edu.harvard.integer.service.managementobject.snmp

Interface SnmpManagerInterface

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BaseManagerInterface
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    SnmpManagerLocalInterface, SnmpManagerRemoteInterface
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SnmpManager

    public interface SnmpManagerInterface
extends BaseManagerInterface
    The SNMP Manager is responsible for importing MIB's into the system. Getting the import MIBs or SNMP OIDs from the database.
